testsuite.name: findLatestTwoByFilters

testcase.name: should respect all filters when determining latest two
should return NULL salary records when filter is null - critical null handling
should return only one record when only one exists
should return NULL experience level records when filter is null - critical null handling
should return the two most recent records in descending order
should return empty list when no records exist
should limit results to exactly two records when more exist
should return empty when filters match no records
should handle all filter combinations correctly
